      "role": "user",
      "content": "u said it's a \"proven fact\" that they work though. isnt that a bit of a stretch? i've seen plenty of people say the data is super messy and that crime goes up in places where guns are restricted because criminals dont follow laws anyway. why do u say they definitely work?",
